    "book_id": "EZR",
    "book_name": "Ezra",
    "chapter": 2,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "Nebuchadnezzar had taken many Jews away from the land of Judah. He had forced them to go to Babylonia as prisoners. Now they returned to Jerusalem and Judah. All of them went back to their own towns. Nebuchadnezzar was king of Babylonia."
  },
  {
